caption:
@MiaGlastonbury and I have been up in the skies with the @Westpac Rescue Helicopter crew in Newcastle to learn more about the incredible work they do.

The service nationally covers over 84% of the Australian population during the summer months with an operation, Australia wide, of 17 helicopters flying from 13 bases. The Service also includes two rescue boats, based in the Northern Territory and Victoria.

We're stoked to support the Service and help out in our own way.

Check out the link in my profile to see how you can do your bit too!

#AirRescue.
